title: Christ T - On Air
seo_description: The Song "On Air" carries a tone of appreciation of what the Gospel of Christ has been doing so far to the global church (Body of Christ) and how God is transiting and building up many believers around the globe who have received the word, their Messenger, Prophet, Teacher or Pastor who came with a unique revelation of Christ for their transformation thereby causing a gradual change in the lives of many Christians.
